query: mutation ($enterprise_id: ID! $organization_name: String! $admin_logins: [String!]! $billing_email: String!) { createEnterpriseOrganization(input: { enterpriseId: $enterprise_id login: $organization_name billingEmail: $billing_email profileName: $organization_name adminLogins: $admin_logins }) { enterprise { name } organization { id name } } }
